{"tid":1088582,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【獲權威認可】武磊登陸西甲後首個獎項！獲世界足球大會傑出表現獎","createTime":"2019-04-02T07:13:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-02T13:30:02.000Z","uid":173952,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"543651f031a84d9fa7f00c2871d346334ff44151","tid":1088582,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:13:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xv96ZkA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxv96ZkA.jpg&h=4af1fcb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港時間4月2日，西班牙足協官網和愛斯賓奴球會官方透露，在本月進行的世界足球大會上，武磊將會獲得獎項表彰。<br />\n  世界足球大會於本月12日在巴塞隆拿舉行，該項會議旨在獎勵在全世界範圍內有著傑出表現的運動員，他們的表現也獲得了西班牙足球的認可。<br />\n  雖然大會尚未進行，但西班牙足協官網和愛斯賓奴足球球會已經確認武磊將會獲獎，這也是他登陸西甲之後獲得的首個獎項。<br />\n  今季武磊在西甲登場8次，攻入1球並有1次助攻。"},{"pid":"48d979d1850bd43a53bd3affc46e6ad148c54e4a","tid":1088582,"uid":213217,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:14:47.000Z","msg":"最佳促進收視獎？"},{"pid":"d98f4cb16a5af5a6b141e08b58d616a3aae6e5b0","tid":1088582,"uid":2111,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T09:55:21.000Z","msg":"人地拎到唔想拎個啲獎<br />\n支那人當寶拎黎打飛機"},{"pid":"ca016c5a0efd87ec0fa691433214b24fbdf936da","tid":1088582,"uid":203961,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"d98f4cb16a5af5a6b141e08b58d616a3aae6e5b0","tid":1088582,"uid":2111,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T09:55:21.000Z","msg":"人地拎到唔想拎個啲獎<br />\n支那人當寶拎黎打飛機"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T10:03:19.000Z","msg":"成日話人玻璃心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你咪又係自己衝出黎 敏感到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4668513f756bcbd3bafaf22685ebe67f151068fa","tid":1088582,"uid":67225,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ca016c5a0efd87ec0fa691433214b24fbdf936da","tid":1088582,"uid":203961,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"quote":{"pid":"d98f4cb16a5af5a6b141e08b58d616a3aae6e5b0","tid":1088582,"uid":211